WelcomeApp.title: Welcome to your new Plesk WordPress Server
WelcomeApp.subtitle: These are your first steps with Plesk
WelcomeApp.lead: Great to meet you! My name is Elvis Plesky, I will assist you in the beginning of your journey with Plesk.  You made the right decision with the WordPress Server if you want to use the best Open-Source CMS WordPress for your projects! Let me help you to get started. Don't worry, it's easy with Plesk - and my help!
